file.name: item.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Example API
paths:
  '/v1/resource':
    get:
      operationId: getResource
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Item'
components:
  schemas:
    Item:
      type: object
      properties:
        mandatoryInteger:
          type: integer
        mandatoryString:
          type: string
        mandatoryEnum:
          type: string
          enum:
            - 'one option'
            - 'another option'
        mandatoryDate:
          type: string
          format: 'date-time'
        mandatoryNullableDate:
          type: string
          format: 'date-time'
          nullable: true
        mandatoryFloat:
          type: number
          format: float
        mandatoryBoolean:
          type: boolean
        mandatoryArray:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
        mandatoryArrayWithMinItems:
          type: array
          minItems: 1
          items:
            type: string
        mandatoryObject:
          type: object
          properties:
            string:
              type: string
            nullableObject:
              type: object
              properties:
                string:
                  type: string
        mandatoryNullableObjectWithAllOf:
          allOf:
            - $ref: '#/components/schemas/EmbeddedObject'
            - type: object
              nullable: true
        mandatoryMixed: {}
        mandatoryAnyOf:
          anyOf:
            - type: number
            - type: string
        nullableObject:
          type: object
          properties:
            string:
              type: string
          nullable: true
        nullableDate:
          type: string
          format: 'date-time'
          nullable: true
        optionalInteger:
          type: integer
        optionalString:
          type: string
        optionalEnum:
          type: string
          enum:
            - 'one option'
            - 'another option'
        optionalIntEnum:
          type: integer
          enum:
            - 0
            - 1
            - 2
        optionalDate:
          type: string
          format: 'date-time'
        optionalFloat:
          type: number
          format: float
        optionalBoolean:
          type: boolean
        optionalArray:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
        optionalMixedArray:
          type: array
          items: {}
        optionalArrayWithMinMaxItems:
          type: array
          minItems: 1
          maxItems: 5
          items:
            type: string
        optionalStringWithMinMaxLength:
          type: string
          minLength: 1
          maxLength: 5
        optionalStringWithPattern:
          type: string
          pattern: ^\d{3}-\d{2}-\d{4}$
          example: 123-45-6789
        optionalIntegerBetweenIncluded:
          type: integer
          minimum: 0
          maximum: 5
        optionalIntegerBetweenExcluded:
          type: integer
          minimum: 0
          maximum: 5
          exclusiveMinimum: true
          exclusiveMaximum: true
        optionalNumberBetweenIncluded:
          type: number
          minimum: 0
          maximum: 5
        optionalNumberBetweenExcluded:
          type: number
          minimum: 0
          maximum: 5
          exclusiveMinimum: true
          exclusiveMaximum: true
        optionalObject:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/EmbeddedObject'
      required:
        - mandatoryInteger
        - mandatoryString
        - mandatoryEnum
        - mandatoryDate
        - mandatoryNullableDate
        - mandatoryFloat
        - mandatoryBoolean
        - mandatoryArray
        - mandatoryArrayWithMinItems
        - mandatoryObject
        - mandatoryNullableObjectWithAllOf
        - mandatoryMixed
        - mandatoryAnyOf
    EmbeddedObject:
      type: object
      properties:
        string:
          type: string
